{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u275dRevenge and Correcting Old Sins Come Together in One Entity\u275e</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/extras/Gif002.gif?t=1739572756\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Revenge Crystal </strong>is an epic top-down action RPG. You explore a defeated world by unknown invaders as an amnesiac knight who must save the world and defeat the invaders by navigating through a world of interconnected challenges, fierce enemies, and intricate puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a rich, diverse world, bursting with secrets and dangers in every unique environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in epic battles with fierce enemies and powerful bosses, testing your combat skills to the max.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wield magical spells with the option to enhance them with elemental powers for devastating effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on intriguing side quests that deepen the lore and add layers to your adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft your own journey, making choices that determine your path and the challenges you face.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your character to suit your playstyle, evolving skills and abilities to conquer your foes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/extras/Gif01.gif?t=1739572756\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a darkened cell, an unknown knight wakes up after a long sleep, on a strange call commands him to end this nightmare. He has no memory of his past, and his body is affected by strange crystals. He starts his journey in a destroyed world under control of unknown invaders. He attempts to find out who he is and why he feels the need for revenge. During his journey filled with challenges and enemies everywhere, he will be forced to face his past secrets and the sins of his people, known as the &quot;Crystallne&quot;, who caused the destruction of several worlds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/extras/SGif03.gif?t=1739572756\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2713680?t=1739572756","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739572756","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/dc4a7709fd33ee2d8becfee5763a9399cd9fb704/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739572756","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/dc4a7709fd33ee2d8becfee5763a9399cd9fb704/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739572756","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3495260,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u275dRevenge and Correcting Old Sins Come Together in One Entity\u275e</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713680/extras/Gif002.gif?t=1739572756\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Revenge Crystal </strong>is an epic top-down action RPG. You explore a defeated world by unknown invaders as an amnesiac knight who must save the world and defeat the invaders by navigating throu